{"tid":1674961,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"舊款Pixel將不會支援Live HDR+、Dual Exposure Controls功能","createTime":"2019-10-25T14:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T03:28:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f3b562ffebece3a91500c0cf72f6d14a91a36e","tid":1674961,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fdn.gsmarena.com/imgroot/news/19/10/pixel-live-hdr-dual-sliders-not-coming-to-older-models//gsmarena_000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffdn.gsmarena.com%2Fimgroot%2Fnews%2F19%2F10%2Fpixel-live-hdr-dual-sliders-not-coming-to-older-models%2F%2Fgsmarena_000.jpg&h=763109a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全新的Google Pixel 4系列已經推出，當中主打的Live HDR+、Dual Exposure Controls功能讓用戶可以實時預覽HDR效果，亦可以分別調整高光、暗位的程度，更容易拍出高動態範圍的照片，不少手持舊款Pixel的用戶都十分期待能透過系統更新獲得新功能，但日前官方已經表明兩項新功能均不會支援舊款機，但同屬新功能的Night Sight模式，則會透過更新支援。"},{"pid":"08abcd0f6676dcb8f9f451b7d23afee9c823dbef","tid":1674961,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fb35937ed6716cb4c99c97d11c5595aa719b5c","tid":1674961,"uid":35301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"點樣可以英文界面但又用到廣東話google assistant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fee7554bcd28be3c0b2ace72cde7a770977731","tid":1674961,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01cc1dc346daa373f445960eecc9e7626cddd3e","tid":1674961,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUPo8oT.